<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="praise-vt">praise <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'preɪz/    美 /'preɪz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>赞扬；称赞：</strong></h4>
<p>反 criticise </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The teacher praised his good homework. 
老师表扬他作业做得好。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was <strong>highly praised for</strong> his research on heart disease.
他因对心脏病的研究而获得了高度的赞扬。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The Smiths are praised <strong><em>_</em></strong>__ the way they bring up their children.   （2013 山东改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. for  </p></div>